  "keyFeatures": [
    "90+ evaluation metrics covering perceptual quality, intelligibility, and technical measurements",
    "Support for multiple input formats (file paths, SCP files, Kaldi-style ARKs)",
    "Built-in distributed evaluation with Slurm integration",
    "Interactive visualization and result analysis tools",
    "Seamless integration with ESPnet and other speech toolkits",
    "Flexible configuration system with YAML-based metric selection"
